                        "@type": "Answer",
                        text: "The walking boot and crutches are essential. The night splint is highly recommended for sleep comfort and safety. Other items significantly improve quality of life during recovery but aren't strictly necessary.",
                    },
                },
            ],
        },
    ],
};
